data.name: label4.Text
data.value: The TechQuint Employee Management System helps admins easily manage employee data, including adding, deleting, and updating records. Admins can generate PDF reports and manage payroll with salary payments and receipts. The dashboard shows key stats like total employees, departments, and pending payroll tasks for a quick overview.

data.name: label11.Text
data.value:
Employee Management: Add, delete, and update employee records.
PDF Reports & Receipts: Generate and print employee details, department reports, and payroll receipts.
Payroll Management: Process salary payments and generate payment receipts.
Department Management: Add and delete departments.
Dashboard: Track real-time activities with stats on employees, departments, and pending payroll tasks.
